<bibRefCitation author="Vikberg, V." journalOrPublisher="Entomologica Fennica" pageId="0" pageNumber="1168" pagination="129 - 172" title="Taxonomy of the species of Eupontaniacrassipes- and Eupontaniaaquilonis-groups (Hymenoptera: Tenthredinidae: Nematinae)" volume="14" year="2003">Vikberg (2003)</bibRefCitation>
