<bibRefCitation author="Vikberg, V." journalOrPublisher="Beitraege zur Entomologie" pageId="0" pageNumber="1168" pagination="239 - 268" title="On the taxonomy and the host plants of North European species of Eupontania (Hymenoptera: Tenthredinidae: Nematinae)" volume="56" year="2006">Vikberg and Zinovjev (2006)</bibRefCitation>
